headline: Agilent Announces Cash Dividend of 24.8 Cents per Share
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., September 17, 2025--Agilent Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced a quarterly dividend of 24.8 cents per share of common stock. The quarterly dividend will be paid on Oct. 22, 2025, to all shareholders of record as of the close of business on Sept. 30, 2025.
